0:16:06.160,0:16:12.500
Mimi ni  yule Mungu anayemsema, ninacho kile ambacho Mungu anasema niwe nacho, naweza kufanya kile Mungu anasema nifanye.

0:16:12.500,0:16:19.320
Hii ndiyo maana ya kuridhika.

0:16:19.320,0:16:23.240
Je, wewe umeridhikai?

0:16:23.240,0:16:28.520
Daima unajilinganisha na kujipima na wengine.

0:16:28.520,0:16:30.720
Hivyo sivyo kuridhika.

0:16:30.720,0:16:33.860
Wivu, wivu.....

0:16:33.860,0:16:37.200
barabara kuelekea mwaka mpya.

0:16:37.200,0:16:41.980
Nataka nikurudishe nyuma nikupe  muhtasari.

0:16:41.980,0:16:57.060
Upendo ni silaha kubwa - basi Acha Upendo Ukuongoze.

0:16:57.060,0:17:14.140
Kile unachotoa sio muhimu kama  namna ambayo wewe unatoa.

0:17:14.140,0:17:24.680
Niambie - wakati unatoa kitu kwa jirani na kusema, "Asante kwa kupokea zawadi yangu" ...

0:17:24.680,0:17:30.100
Wakati mtu anapata zawadi yako, ni kutengeneza hatima yako.

0:17:30.100,0:17:31.480
Ni kukusaidia wewe.

0:17:31.480,0:17:39.260
Wewe humsaidii mtu yule unayempa zawadi bali yule anayepokea zawadi anakusaidia wewe.

0:17:39.260,0:17:44.760
Leo, unaamini kuwa yule mtu unayempa zawadi ndiye unae msaidiea na anatakiwa kukushukuru.

0:17:44.760,0:17:49.220
Badala yake, ni lazima kumshukuru yule anayepokea zawadi yako.

0:17:49.220,0:17:53.340
Wakati wa kutoa, wewe unaandaa hatima yako.

0:17:53.340,0:17:58.020
Ibada ya Jumapili SCOAN

