0:19:23.800,0:19:31.980
Kama nikisema unatakiwa kunipa mimi, hakitabarikiwa, kwasababu hutoi kutoka moyoni.

0:19:31.980,0:19:35.460
Si kitu unapaswa kunijulisha au nikumbusha.

0:19:35.460,0:19:38.300
Inatakiwa itoke moyoni.

0:19:38.300,0:19:40.680
Sio jambo la kulazimisha.

0:19:40.680,0:19:42.160
Ni baraka.

0:19:42.160,0:19:50.240
Hatulazimishi watu kutoa baraka; baraka huja kwa njia ya kawaida.

0:19:50.240,0:19:53.960
Ibada ya Jumapili SCOAN

